name: BMO S&P/TSX 60 Index ETF
longDescription: The BMO S&P/TSX 60 Index ETF has been designed to replicate, to the extent possible, the performance of the S&P/TSX 60 Index, net of expenses. The ETF invests in and holds the Constituent Securities of the Index in the same proportion as they are reflected in the Index. The BMO SPTSX 6 Index ETF has been designed to replicate, to the extent possible, the performance of the SPTSX 6 Index, net of expenses.
